Package: shintodb
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Shinto DB Connections, Config Management
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Remko Duursma
Maintainer: Remko Duursma <remko@shintolabs.nl>
Description: Everything to work with PostgresDB in Shinto apps.
  Manage, encrypt, and decrypt config files. Database R6 layer with
  generic methods. Manage database connections automatically.
